data.title: 2017 Donors Childrens Friend
data.meta_description: This page is a complete list of gifts made by our generous donors for 2017, these gifts make it possible for us to support at-risk children.
data.text:
Thank You For Your Financial Support in 2017

Donors listed as of 12/31/2017. If we’ve made a mistake… we’re terribly sorry. If we have inadvertently left out, misspelled, or misrepresented your gift, please contact Owen Heleen, Interim Chief of Philanthropy at oheleen@cfsri.org or 401.808.5277.
